NOTES ON THE BOOKS REFERENCED

The methodologies discussed in this repository are summarized and adapted
from published books, whose copyright belongs to their respective authors
and publishers. This repository contains:

- Editorial interpretation and structural reorganization of public methods
- AI interaction design built around those methods
- No verbatim reproduction of book text beyond fair use

If an author or publisher believes any skill in this repository infringes
their rights, please file a GitHub issue. We will remove or revise the
content immediately.
